t: "Gom…óii Men nulirii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen …ìanngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani …ìe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ìe …ìen √±ii…ìira e nun…óal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yim…ìe …ìen, e no Allah fe√±√±inira …ìen walloo…ìe Mo e Nulaa…óo Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Foolu…óo. @Corrected"